# grapher_mixed_relations_smoke.numos — Phase 10D. Three slots of different kinds
# in one grapher: f0 sin(x) (explicit), f1 x^2+y^2=4 (implicit circle), f2
# x^2+y^2<1 (inequality disk). Screenshots the layered Graph, then the Table.
# Proves: (a) explicit curve + implicit contour + shaded inequality region all
# render together; (b) the Table shows real values for the explicit column and a
# graceful "--" for the implicit/inequality columns (never "nan"). Warning-only.
log "mixed relations: start"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
key down
key enter
key sin
key x
key right
key enter
wait 30
key down
key enter
key x
key ^
key 2
key right
key +
key y
key ^
key 2
key right
key =
key 4
key enter
wait 30
key down
key enter
key x
key ^
key 2
key right
key +
key y
key ^
key 2
key right
key lt
key 1
key enter
wait 60
key graph
wait 120
screenshot out/grapher_mixed_relations_graph.ppm
key table
wait 120
screenshot out/grapher_mixed_relations_table.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "mixed relations: graph+table ok"
